{"tid":827191,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"明報：本報接獲消息，高鐵上月試車曾發生事故但沒公布","createTime":"2018-09-18T18:49:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-23T12:37:45.000Z","uid":5195,"like":365,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":77,"replies":[{"pid":"cb9df8922db721ed0990a29911c74e976ca04322","tid":827191,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T18:49:06.000Z","msg":"明報頭條搶先睇<br />\n<br />\n【偵查報道】本報接獲消息，高鐵香港段上月試車時曾發生事故但沒有公布，一塊兩呎長的鋼製指示牌，懷疑抵受不住列車高速行駛時產生的氣流，整塊被扯至飛脫，扭曲變形。據了解，機電署即時派員調查，事後罕有要求港鐵加固全線所有同類指示牌。有工程師認為事故屬設計失誤。立法會議員擔心，若指示牌曾被列車輾過而嚴重扭曲，屬嚴重事故，質疑港鐵及政府隱瞞&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.postimg.cc/NGxL58L6/42134400_1980968905296568_704690827741364224_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.postimg.cc%2FNGxL58L6%2F42134400_1980968905296568_704690827741364224_n.jpg&h=b70fbec4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6975a44041fdac23c1f88f63f54cd31916ee727e","tid":827191,"uid":144738,"like":161,"dislike":0,"score":161,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T18:52:17.000Z","msg":"一定係塊牌廢得濟先甩落嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df3c4a1f3810511b2938a7bcfa5d23055c19ea87","tid":827191,"uid":24788,"like":35,"dislike":2,"score":33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T18:52:46.000Z","msg":"同大陸接軌"},{"pid":"a51cefa776ec3de1231c6f1991c303115fcbe6ef","tid":827191,"uid":7699,"like":57,"dislike":0,"score":57,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T18:53:26.000Z","msg":"快啲通車啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3df8597924b77922906d79b248545a65ef5689bf","tid":827191,"uid":187956,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T18:57:10.000Z","msg":"係塊牌撞到架車 架車冇事 表示安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72a1cdb8de6e62496bf3e7343d1bc5ac66490569","tid":827191,"uid":203431,"like":72,"dislike":1,"sc